metadata.name: Village 1 modified
metadata.description:
° When I was bored in front of the computer and not knowing what to do, I found my drawing that I had done 11 years ago.  
I began to modify it and little by little I saw how it took shape, a landscape of a town that took me more than a month to finish and understand that:  
"Beauty is in the consciousness of the one who looks closely and enjoys what he sees."

° Cuando me encontraba frente al computador aburrido y sin saber que hacer, me encontré con mi dibujo que avía realizado ase 11 años.  
Empecé modificarlo y vi poco a poco como tomaba forma, un paisaje de un pueblo que me llevo mas de un mes en terminarlo y comprender que:  
" La belleza esta en la conciencia del que mira detenidamente y disfruta de lo que ve ".
